generate second-level responses with taxonomy under DINA

generate_X_tax2.Rd

generate second-level responses with taxonomy under DINA

generate_X_tax2(X1_sub, A_set20, D_mat, p_short, Q2, c, g, model = "DINA")

Arguments

X1_sub

The subset of individuals who has one particular level 1 latent attributes
A_set20

The true leve 2 set of latent attributes
D_mat

J1 by J2 matrix for indicating the tree structure
p_short

level 2 sparse population level prevalences
Q2

level 2 Q in a subset of level 1 latent attributes
c

1-slipping parameters
g

guess parameters
model

"DINA" (default); "DINO"

Value

  • X2 level 2 observed responses

  • Z latent attribute profiles for all individuals at level 2

  • X_true2 Ideal response matrix
